graph TB
    subgraph "Llama Stack K8s Operator"
        Controller[Operator Controller Manager<br/>Deployment]
        LLSDController[LlamaStackDistribution Controller<br/>Watches CRDs]
        KustomizeEngine[Kustomize-based Deployment Engine<br/>Manifest Generation]
        FeatureFlags[Feature Flags Manager<br/>ConfigMap]
        ImageMapper[Distribution Image Mapper<br/>ConfigMap]
        NetworkTransformer[Network Policy Transformer<br/>Plugin]

        Controller -->|manages| LLSDController
        LLSDController -->|uses| KustomizeEngine
        LLSDController -->|reads| FeatureFlags
        LLSDController -->|reads| ImageMapper
        KustomizeEngine -->|uses| NetworkTransformer
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        LLSDCR[LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>llamastack.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Managed Resources"
        Deployment[Llama Stack Deployment]
        Service[Llama Stack Service<br/>8321/TCP]
        PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>Model Storage]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>Optional]
        Ingress[Ingress<br/>Optional Route]
        ServiceAccount[ServiceAccount]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor]
        InferenceProvider[Inference Provider<br/>Ollama/vLLM/TGI]
        ContainerRegistry[Container Registry<br/>docker.io/quay.io]
        HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub<br/>Model Downloads]
    end

    subgraph "Internal RHOAI Integration"
        Monitoring[OpenShift Monitoring<br/>ServiceMonitor CRD]
        SCC[Security Context Constraints<br/>anyuid]
    end

    User[User] -->|creates| LLSDCR
    LLSDCR -->|watched by| LLSDController

    LLSDController -->|creates/updates| Deployment
    LLSDController -->|creates| Service
    LLSDController -->|creates| PVC
    LLSDController -->|creates| NetworkPolicy
    LLSDController -->|creates| Ingress
    LLSDController -->|creates| ServiceAccount

    Controller -->|reconciles via| K8sAPI
    Controller -->|exposes metrics to| Prometheus

    Deployment -->|pulls images from| ContainerRegistry
    Deployment -->|runs| InferenceProvider
    InferenceProvider -->|downloads models from| HuggingFace

    Controller -->|integrates| Monitoring
    Deployment -->|uses| SCC

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LLSDController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style LLSDCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style InferenceProvider fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ContainerRegistry fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Monitoring fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style SCC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
